016package de.cuioss.uimodel.nameprovider.data;
017
018import java.io.Serializable;
019import java.util.Map;
020import java.util.Map.Entry;
021
022import lombok.EqualsAndHashCode;
023import lombok.NonNull;
024import lombok.ToString;
025
026/**
027 * Entry data implements {@linkplain Entry} interface which can be used for
028 * transformation to be added in {@linkplain Map}
029 *
030 * @author Eugen Fischer
031 * @param <K> bounded type for Key must extends {@linkplain Serializable}
032 * @param <V> bounded type for Value must extends {@linkplain Serializable}
033 */
034@ToString(doNotUseGetters = true)
035@EqualsAndHashCode(doNotUseGetters = true)
036public class EntryData<K extends Serializable, V extends Serializable> implements Entry<K, V>, Serializable {
037
038    private static final long serialVersionUID = -6403178000941411123L;
039
040    private final K key;
041
042    private V value;
043
044    /**
045     * @param key must not be {@code null}
046     */
047    public EntryData(@NonNull final K key) {
048        this.key = key;
049    }
050
051    /**
052     * @param key   must not be {@code null}
053     * @param value
054     */
055    public EntryData(final K key, final V value) {
056        this(key);
057        setValue(value);
058    }
059
060    @Override
061    public K getKey() {
062        return key;
063    }
064
065    @Override
066    public V getValue() {
067        return value;
068    }
069
070    @Override
071    public V setValue(V value) {
072        this.value = value;
073        return this.value;
074    }
075
076}
